TEXT.S: = Tatoba' = Gaga mniq Sincuseyn Ufungsyang ka alang Tatoba'. 159 sapah ka kneegu na sapah, 407 hiyi ka kana knhbragan na hiyi. Tnpusu seejiq o mangal 88% niqan 360 hiyi sp, rahuq na uxay tnpusu seejiq o mangal 12% niqan 47 hiyi koia. Kana ka kleegan seejiq ga, Tayal 60%, Saysiyat 27%, Amis 1%.
